distraction: No; I was fully focused on the experiment. The experiment required my full attention; and I didn't want to make a mistake
strategies: I used the story idea for sure and helped; of course I had to make it as whacky as possible to help me remember. I also thought about the color changes in beats to make sure I wait for the color before pressing 1 or 2.
easier: I think so; for instance the globe and the dust collector were easiest for me to memorize and from there; the other objects fell into the story I created around the objects.
comments: This was a very interesting experiment. It was challenging in the beginning but not as difficult as I thought it was going to be. It was fun.
